Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:16.88,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}If I spend more time alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:21.30,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I thought I would get used to it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:27.42,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I'm a coward with a a straight face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:32.24,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,223)\be2}But in reality I was afraid inside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:37.06,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}It shouldn't have been like this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:42.47,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Only excuses keep piling up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:48.80,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I will be forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.85,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}From your memory someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:23:01.53,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}For a few more decades let's go for a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:06.06,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}To collect the things that have been dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:11.18,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}No matter what my future is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:14.51,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}But I'm not going
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:19.86,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}To stop my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:25.85,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Someday I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:32.35,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Meet you again
